      "para_id": "Q004970.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Ibbi-Suen , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Lu-Ninĝirsu , the scribe , child of Lu-Bau , is your servant ."
    }
